Package: ImmuneLENS
Type: Package
Title: Immune Lymphocyte Estimation from Nucleotide Sequencing
Version: 1.0.1
Author: Robert Bentham
Maintainer: Robert Bentham <robert.bentham.11@ucl.ac.uk>
Description: Immune Lymphocyte Estimation from Nucleotide Sequencing (Immune LENS) is an R package to calculate T and B cell fractions from WGS or WES data from hg19 or hg38 aligned genomes. Includes functions from TcellExTRECT package for support of WES analysis.
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0),
    gratia
